    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>Sorcerers who serve in the sun goddess's court display powers infused with the glory of the sun itself.</p><p><b>Class Skill: </b>Perception</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>searing light (3rd), fury of the sunARG (5th), daylight (7th), shield of dawnISG (9th), flame strike (11th), true seeing (13th), sunbeam (15th), sunburst (17th), overwhelming presenceUM (19th).</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Alertness, Combat Casting, Empower Spell, Improved Initiative, Lightning Reflexes, Quicken Spell, Spell Focus, Spell Penetration.</p><p><b>Bloodline Arcana: </b>Whenever you cast a spell with the fire descriptor, if it deals damage, it deals +1 point of damage per die rolled.</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>The solar power that infuses your being alters the way you interact with the world, searing through your spells.</p>",
